      "name": "Skill",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">Anemo DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/25/25750596/1ce09211f025bf5470682189e0837732_7661976531873764800.png",
                "id": "talent62090",
                "key": "Yuuban Meigen",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Yuuban Meigen"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 2 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo DMG</span>. Karakter ini memperoleh status <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Windfavored</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Windfavored</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Saat Karakter yang terpengaruh menggunakan Normal Attack: </span>Mengakibatkan DMG +2. Jika lawan masih memiliki Karakter standby, maka Skill ini akan mengakibatkan DMG terhadap Karakter Standby lawan berikutnya.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan: 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/25/25750596/052cd901b44cef8359f0bebb98404194_357304804892742316.png",
                "id": "talent22363",
                "key": "Hanega: Song of the Wind",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Hanega: Song of the Wind"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 7 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo DMG</span>.</p><p>Jika Karakter memiliki status <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Windfavored</span>, maka akan menghapus status tersebut dan mengakibatkan DMG +1 tambahan.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Windfavored</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Saat Karakter yang terpengaruh menggunakan Normal Attack: </span>Mengakibatkan DMG +2. Jika lawan masih memiliki Karakter standby, maka Skill ini akan mengakibatkan DMG terhadap Karakter Standby lawan berikutnya.</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Penggunaan: 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/25/25750596/5a55e705974f27b8bb86c628019d5ad9_1706220966177217442.png",
                "id": "talent26050",
                "key": "Kyougen: Five Ceremonial Plays",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Kyougen: Five Ceremonial Plays"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Bereaksi dengan Elemen jika sudah diberikan:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Cryo Swirl</span>: Mengakibatkan 1 poin Cryo DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Hydro Swirl</span>: Mengakibatkan 1 poin Hydro DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Pyro Swirl</span>: Mengakibatkan 1 poin Pyro DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro Swirl</span>: Mengakibatkan 1 poin Electro DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/25/25750596/c97292d96456bfe4abeca16bfce801e4_580242575836252818.png",
                "id": "talent80746",
                "key": "Anemo DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Anemo DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Penggunaan</span></strong></p><p>Setelah efek kartu ini dipicu, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span>-nya akan dikonsumsi.</p><p>Kartu ini akan langsung dibuang setelah semua <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span> telah dikonsumsi.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/25/25750596/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_2917748610435357687.png",
